  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You conjure a brightly burning orb of light in one unoccupied space within range. The star sheds bright light in a 30 foot radius and dim light for an additional 30 feet.</p><p>When you cast this spell, you designate any number of creatures you see as friendly. A friendly creature within the bright light of this spell has advantage on saving throws against spells.</p><p>As a bonus action while the spell lasts, you can make a <strong>ranged spell attack</strong> against up to three different creatures in the light of this spell. On a hit, you deal <strong>4d6 radiant damage</strong> to the target. You have advantage on the attack roll if the target is in the area of bright light.</p>",
